title: Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli Ep 1: Going Deep with Eddie Bravo
description:
Welcome to the inaugural episode of The Tin Foil Hat podcast! For the first episode I've decide to bring on Eddie Bravo. After some technical difficulties we talk about.....
1) Why people do not believe Conspiracies
2) Dinosaurs
3) Russian Hacks
4) Hillary Clinton
Please let me know what you think about the podcast. Should I do more or just end it right here? Le the know!
